Package com.intellij.execution.configurations

Class ParametersList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.execution.configurations.ParametersList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public final class ParametersList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    A list of command-line parameters featuring the following:
    • special handling for Java properties (-D<name>=<value>)
    • macro substitution upon addition for plain parameters, and property values
    • named groups for parameters
    • parameter strings with quoted parameters
    See Also:
    defineProperty(String, String), expandMacros(String), addParamsGroup(String), addParametersString(String), ParamsGroup
